Comparing against `docs/specs/BACKUP_STRATEGY_INITIAL.md`:

| Responsibility | Required by Policy | Current Implementation |
|---------------|-------------------|------------------------|
| Monthly baseline snapshot | YES | NO — runs a daily full backup, no monthly concept |
