- Model mismatch: daily full vs. tiered (monthly baseline + nightly incremental)
- Storage mismatch: R2 (cloud) vs. local
- Retention mismatch: 30 days vs. 6 months
- Encryption mismatch: implemented vs. policy-deferred

These gaps are implementation-level mismatches between strongbox's current behavior and the canonical policy. They are tracked in `docs/milestones.md` as future work. They do not affect the invocation gap findings above.

